_sText:
My random escape map with my ideas. Escape from undergound and city17 to airport.
funny traps (heli) lava earthquakes and water included.
Test, rate and comment!
And also report bugs if you find something.



Music: Call Of Duty: Modern Warware 2 Soundtrack

Update beta2:
- Trucks leaves when zombie reach top of volcano
- CTs can´t camp top of volcano
- Added one defend point
- 64 spawnpoints
- train goes little faster
- Added arrows to City17
- Plane fixed
- and other little bugs also fixed.


Update beta3:
- Cts cant proceed until zombie reach top of volcano
- Props in helitrap is deleted
- added more defence time
- added invisible blocks to volcano´s edges

Update beta4:
- Helitrap is easier to pass
- Fixed my mistakes
- Final bridges are smaller
- Flying cars have deleted
- Fixed glitchs
- "Cts cant proceed until zombie reach top of volcano" now works

Update beta5:
- Fixed that helitrap cant pass
- added elevator defence point
- Water removed from tunnel
- Firts zombie block bug is fixed

Note: I dont make this much look better because i have other things also to do
And if this goes to some zombieserver write ip to comments

(Next version might be final)
